divs: Sighting DetailsI saw an object in the sky, that caught my eye. it did't look like a plane. There was a white light on it that was on. and a red and blue flashing lights. the object was moving from left to right in the sky. I started watching it and then after a few seconds the object just disappeared. i watched in the sky for 15 more minutes to see if it reappeared and i didnt see anything... no lights, nothing. a few minutes after it disappeared, i saw a plane or something come from the other direction, it had a white light, and fly right by where the other object had disappeared from. strange. could have just been planes... but who knows...
Summary: Blue, white and red light object, disappears.
